author: Warhammer
description:
Dan and Jake have been set the challenge of completing an army each in just five days! Will they be able to complete the task? What will they create? Did Jake understand the task? Will Dan get the footsloggers finished? Find out in this wild race against time! 

Here’s a list of the paints we used in today’s video:

DAN
Contrast:
Black Legion 
Blood Angels Red
Flesh Tearers Red
Nazdreg Yellow

Base:
Death Guard Green
Iron Warriors 

Layer:
Stormhost Silver
Ulthuan Grey

Shades:
Agrax Earthshade
Mortarion Grime 

JAKE
Contrast:
Gore-Grunta Fur

Base:
Averland Sunset
Balthasar Gold
Barak-Nar Burgundy
Deathworld Forest
Steel Legion Drab
Warplock Bronze
XV-88

Layer:
Blue Horror
Dechala Lilac
Kakophoni Purple
Ironbreaker
Ionrach Skin
Wild Rider Red
World Bearers Red

Shade:
Targor Rageshade
Soulblight Grey

Technical:
Lahmium Medium

Tools:
M Shade Brush STC
M Base Brush STC
M Drybrush STC
M Shade Brush STC
S Drybrush STC 
XS Artificer Brush
